single-file, dark-mode â€œLC Unified 4.5â€ app that bundles the whole toolkit in one HTML:
Field Guide (import/search/bundle/print/JSON), Case Journal, Clause Bank, Mock Hearing, and Settings â€” all offline, no dependencies. It also ships with an embedded Markdown preload block so you can bake in FG 1â€“1000.
Save as LC-Unified-4.5.html, open locally.
