Quick start
	â€¢	Open LC-Unified-4.5.html â†’ Field Guide â†’ either Use Embedded (preload) or Import MD and paste your full FG 1â€“1000.
	â€¢	Filter/search, Add to bundle, then Copy/Export/Print as needed.
	â€¢	Use Journal for dated case notes; Clause Bank to save reusable paragraphs; Mock Hearing for a countdown + scratchpad that can pull your bundleâ€™s model lines.
	â€¢	Settings â†’ Backup exports everything as JSON; Danger Zone wipes local data.
